sentences.english: Haitian woman crosses a street of Port-au-Prince February 1, 2006.
sentences.chinese: 穿過海地太子港街道的婦女。

sentences.english: A man throws a corpse onto a pile of dead bodies, at the morgue of a hospital in Port-au-Prince.
sentences.chinese: 在太子港一座醫院的停屍處，一名男子拋下一具遺體。

sentences.english: People in Port-au-Prince watch as a French rescue team searches for a survivor.
sentences.chinese: 在太子港人們在看着法國救援隊搜尋一名生還者。

sentences.english: A man ferries wooden boards on a motorcycle in Port-au-Prince, Haiti.
sentences.chinese: 太子港，一名男子在摩托上運送着木板，海地。

sentences.english: Colorful gingerbread houses like this one are scattered throughout Port-au-Prince.
sentences.chinese: 這些色彩豔麗的房子零零散散的分佈在太子港。

sentences.english: He just wanted to go someplace other that back to Port-au-Prince.
sentences.chinese: 除了讓他回到太子港，他現在去那裏都行。

sentences.english: Haiti's prime minister recently said that child traffickers are  targeting the scores of children now on their own in Port au Prince.
sentences.chinese: 海地總理最近稱人販正趁火打劫販賣太子港孤兒。

sentences.english: Most people in Port-au-Prince live in tin shacks .
sentences.chinese: 太子港的大多數居民居住在鐵皮棚裏。

sentences.english: A resident prepares mud cakes at the zone of Cite-Soleil in Port-au-Prince, Haiti.
sentences.chinese: 在太子港索萊伊城地區一個居民在製作泥餅，海地。

sentences.english: Haitians look through a hole in their makeshift home in Port-au-Prince, Haiti.
sentences.chinese: 在太子港海地人通過臨時帳篷的縫口向外看着，海地。

sentences.english: A view of the Canape-Vert area of Port-au-Prince shows hundreds of homes destroyed by the earthquake.
sentences.chinese: 俯瞰太子港，我們可以看到全城現在已經是一篇廢墟。

sentences.english: The body of a woman is trapped under a collapsed building in Bourdon in Port-au-Prince, Haiti, Jan. 18, 2010.
sentences.chinese: 日，在海地太子港，一具遇難婦女屍體被壓在廢墟下。

sentences.english: The main force of the earthquake was felt 17 kilometres south-west of the Haitian capital, Port-au-Prince.
sentences.chinese: 地震震中位於海地首都太子港西南17公里處。
我們現在看到的是太子港。

sentences.english: Port-au-Prince in Haiti ranked at the bottom of this table, Mercer said.
sentences.chinese: 海地首都太子港在生態城市榜單中排在最末。

sentences.english: Haitians wait in line to get water at a makeshift shelter in Port-au-Prince.
sentences.chinese: 在太子港海地人在一間臨時住房排隊等候領水。
